      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Scorching Showdown",
        "Client": "Support Squad Enthusiast",
        "Description": "They may have home advantage but\r\nif you take \u2018em on, we\u0027ll cheer for ya!\r\nReady!? OK! *clap* \u0022We\u0027ve got the\r\npride! We\u0027ve got the spirit! Our hunter\r\nis the best so let \u0027em hear it! K-A-M-\r\nU-R-A! What\u0027s that spell? KAMURA!\r\nKAMURA! Goooooo Kamura!\u0022 Wooo!",
